Prabhu, if I hadn't been here, this fire would've never happened--

90
00:08:03,900 --> 00:08:05,730
林 拜托...
Lin, please. Please.

91
00:08:08,900 --> 00:08:11,030
這里發生火災并不奇怪
Fires, they happen here.

92
00:08:12,740 --> 00:08:16,120
你認為拉克什米的死不讓我難過嗎
You think I'm not hating Lakshmi is gone, huh?

93
00:08:17,700 --> 00:08:18,830
這一次我們已經算幸運
This time, we are lucky.

94
00:08:18,910 --> 00:08:22,080
去年發生過一場更大的火災 貧民區被燒毀的地方更多
Last year, there was much bigger fire, much more of the jhopadpatti was burned.

95
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:23,710
