More than 20 died.

96
00:08:27,750 --> 00:08:29,170
我帶點食物回來 好嗎
I will bring food, okay?

97
00:09:00,660 --> 00:09:02,450
放下...該死...
Drop the-- Fuck. Fuck.

98
