99
00:09:04,790 --> 00:09:06,290
你快啊
Get the fuck on.

100
00:09:08,590 --> 00:09:10,670
別碰任何警報鍵 知道嗎
Don't touch any fucking alarm buttons, all right?

101
00:09:10,670 --> 00:09:12,710
你們幾位女士 能把這些袋子裝滿嗎
Could you ladies fill these bags up, please?

102
00:09:12,800 --> 00:09:15,220
全都有保險的 真的不用擔心
It's all insured. It's really not worth worrying about.

103
00:09:15,220 --> 00:09:16,890
照他說的做吧
Just do what he says.

104
00:09:17,470 --> 00:09:20,060
求你了 勞拉 -好的...
Please... Laura. -Okay, okay, okay.

105
00:09:20,060 --> 00:09:21,850
懶惰的混蛋 為什么不找個工作
Why don't you get a job, you lazy bastards?

106
