嘿 不好意思 這就是我們的工作 肥豬
Hey! Excuse me, this is our job, you fat ass.

107
00:09:26,020 --> 00:09:27,730
別擋我們的道 懂嗎
Don't get in the way of us doing it, all right?

108
00:09:27,810 --> 00:09:31,190
來吧 親愛的 別擔心 你只需要把袋子裝滿
Come on, love. It's all good. You just need to fill the bag.

109
00:09:31,280 --> 00:09:32,860
看不出來她很害怕嗎
Can't you see she's terrified?

110
00:09:32,860 --> 00:09:34,490
把袋子裝滿
Just fill the bag!

111
00:09:42,740 --> 00:09:45,040
讓一讓...
Out of the way! Out of the way! Move! Move!

112
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:52,250
