Hey. Get off me.

115
00:09:59,970 --> 00:10:01,180
把槍放下
Drop the bloody gun.

116
00:10:02,260 --> 00:10:04,180
放開我 混蛋 放下槍
Get off me! Bastard. Drop the gun!

117
00:10:04,980 --> 00:10:06,310
